5005.scepterDescription: Causes Spell Shield to passively block and reflect a targeted spell once every 12 seconds.
5005.name: Spell Shield

5008.scepterDescription: Battle Hunger provides -30% damage output reduction. Applies Battle Hunger on nearby enemies after a successful Culling Blade.
5008.name: Battle Hunger

5011.scepterDescription: Decreases cooldown and makes Brain Sap pierce Spell Immunity.
5011.name: Brain Sap

5018.scepterDescription: Grants 2 charges to Rupture with a 40 seconds replenish time.
5018.name: Rupture

5022.scepterDescription: Causes Drow Ranger's attacks to splinter on the target, hitting nearby units with normal attacks that deal reduced damage.
5022.name: Marksmanship

5024.scepterDescription: Enchant Totem becomes a 900 range ground target ability, causing Earthshaker to jump in the air and land at the target spot, casting Enchant Totem there.  Self-casting the ability will behave in the original form, without jumping.
5024.name: Enchant Totem

5030.scepterDescription: Increases number of slashes and decreases cooldown.
5030.name: Omnislash

5035.scepterDescription: Drags enemies with the Ghostship towards the crash site. Enemies are still able to perform actions while being dragged.
5035.name: Ghostship

5043.scepterDescription: Changes Laguna Blade's damage type to Pure, and allows it to slice through spell immunity.
5043.name: Laguna Blade

5047.scepterDescription: Increases damage. Decreases cooldown. Finger of Death hits all units in a small area.
5047.name: Finger of Death

5051.scepterDescription: Passively triggers Starstorm every 10 seconds. Does not trigger if the enemy doesn't see Mirana.
5051.name: Starstorm

5065.scepterDescription: Causes Spirit Lance to bounce on nearby enemies.
5065.name: Spirit Lance

5073.scepterDescription: Increases damage from coil breaks, increases coil duration, coil break stun goes through spell immunity.
5073.name: Dream Coil

5081.scepterDescription: Causes Serpent Wards to have split shot, attacking two units for full damage. Increases attack range of Serpent Wards.
5081.name: Mass Serpent Ward

5085.scepterDescription: Causes faster strikes that can damage structures as well.  When striking buildings, it will only target towers, barracks, and the Ancient.
5085.name: Eye of the Storm

5089.scepterDescription: If a nearby allied hero is slain, they will be transformed into a wraith and have their death delayed for 7 seconds.
5089.name: Reincarnation

5097.scepterDescription: God's Strength grants bonus damage to allies in a 900 radius.
5097.name: God's Strength

5099.scepterDescription: Electric Vortex affects all enemies within a radius around Storm Spirit.
5099.name: Electric Vortex

5102.scepterDescription: Adds Caustic Finale poison to heroes hit by your Burrowstrike and doubles its cast range. Does not apply Caustic Finale to illusions.
5102.name: Burrowstrike

5118.scepterDescription: Gush becomes a ground targeted wave ability that affects enemy units in a line.  Decreases cooldown.
5118.name: Gush

5125.scepterDescription: Decreases cooldown, allows swapping of non-hero units and causes Vengeful Spirit to spawn a Vengeance Illusion when she dies. Vengeance illusion lasts until she revives and is able to use all of your abilities (but not items).
5125.name: Nether Swap

5129.scepterDescription: Applies Frostbite to any unit that has been standing in the Freezing Field for over 2.5 seconds.
5129.name: Freezing Field

5133.scepterDescription: Reduces cooldown, decreases damage reduction, and removes debuffs from item effects.
5133.name: Focus Fire

5137.scepterDescription: Increases damage and casting range. Removes the limit on the number of times Chain Frost can jump.
5137.name: Chain Frost

5141.scepterDescription: Death Ward attacks have True Strike and bounce between nearby enemies.
5141.name: Death Ward

5145.scepterDescription: Increases duration and allows you to target an allied hero, hiding inside them for the duration.
5145.name: Tricks of the Trade

5149.scepterDescription: Adds the current level of Midnight Pulse to Black Hole.
5149.name: Black Hole

5150.scepterDescription: Causes Laser to refract between all visible enemy units within range.
5150.name: Laser

5157.scepterDescription: Turns Assassinate into a ground target AoE ability, that after the channel period launches a critical strike and procs headshot on units in the AoE. Only affects visible heroes.
5157.name: Assassinate

5165.scepterDescription: Calls 2 Golems with reduced stats and bounty.
5165.name: Chaotic Offering

5221.scepterDescription: Decreases mana cost and cooldown, and increases cast range.
5221.name: Viper Strike

5225.scepterDescription: Allows Luna to cast Eclipse on an allied unit or herself and have its effects follow them, or cast it on an area. Also increases total beams and duration, removes the limit on beams per unit, and makes the beams appear twice as fast.
5225.name: Eclipse

5234.scepterDescription: Causes Shallow Grave to be an AoE spell.
5234.name: Shallow Grave

5243.scepterDescription: While Pulse Nova is active, Lightning Storm will hit one random unit in a radius every 1.75 seconds.
5243.name: Lightning Storm

5248.scepterDescription: Increases damage. If a unit is killed by Wrath of Nature, or within 4 seconds thereafter, a Nature's Call treant will spawn. These treants' health and damage are based on the current level of Nature's Call. If a hero is killed, a Greater Treant will be created, which has 3 times as much health and damage.
5248.name: Wrath of Nature

5258.scepterDescription: Increases the damage dealt by illusions.
5258.name: Wall of Replica

5266.scepterDescription: Increases duration, radius becomes global and affects buildings.
5266.name: Guardian Angel

5270.scepterDescription: Increases attack range, and cast range of Impetus.
5270.name: Impetus

5278.scepterDescription: Grants unobstructed vision in the night. The improved vision does not depend on using Darkness.
5278.name: Darkness

5285.scepterDescription: Allows Shuriken Toss to bounce twice on each hero.
5285.name: Shuriken Toss

5292.scepterDescription: Reduces cooldown, and allows Weaver to cast Time Lapse on an ally.
5292.name: Time Lapse

5300.scepterDescription: Increases flame length, duration, and damage.
5300.name: Macropyre

5323.scepterDescription: Flaming Lasso grabs both its target, as well as the target's nearest allied hero within 400 range. The secondary target is tethered to the first. Also causes Flaming Lasso to deal 100 damage per second.
5323.name: Flaming Lasso

5330.scepterDescription: Allows Holy Persuasion to target Ancient Creeps, maximum one per level of Hand of God.
5330.name: Holy Persuasion

5342.scepterDescription: Increases Doom's duration, and will suspend its duration while the affected unit is within 900 range. Also causes it to remove positive buffs from the target when cast, and break most passive abilities while active.
5342.name: Doom

5356.scepterDescription: Causes the Greater Bash to hit an area around the initial target, decreases cooldown, and increases cast range.
5356.name: Nether Strike

5360.scepterDescription: Reduces cooldown and allows Ursa to use Enrage while disabled.
5360.name: Enrage

5364.scepterDescription: Adds a Side Gunner that at random attacks enemy units within a 600 radius every 1.1 seconds.
5364.name: Call Down

5369.scepterDescription: Alchemist melts down Aghanim's Scepter to grant an allied hero all Aghanim's Scepter upgrades.
5369.name: Chemical Rage

5378.scepterDescription: Causes Glaives to pierce Spell Immunity and deal 100% more damage against silenced units.
5378.name: Glaives of Wisdom

5392.scepterDescription: Grants charges to Astral Imprisonment. Damage areas stack.
5392.name: Astral Imprisonment

5403.scepterDescription: Earth gains Thunder Clap, Storm gains Drunken Haze and Fire gains Drunken Brawler.
5403.name: Primal Split

5425.scepterDescription: Cooldown is removed, replaced with 3 charges that replenish every 40 seconds. Also causes Demonic Purge to break its target's passive abilities while active.
5425.name: Demonic Purge

5429.scepterDescription: Reduces cooldown to %cooldown_scepter% seconds and allows Phantasm to be cast on an allied hero. 1200 Cast Range
5429.name: Phantasm

5437.scepterDescription: When Overgrowth is cast, it is also cast around Eye of the Forest to deal 175 damage per second.
5437.name: Overgrowth

5470.scepterDescription: Song of the Siren regenerates all nearby allies for 10% of their health per second.
5470.name: Song of the Siren

5474.scepterDescription: Permanent Spirit Form. During daytime, grants unobstructed vision, and allows Illuminate to heal allies for the same amount as its damage values.
5474.name: Spirit Form

5479.scepterDescription: Allows Illuminate to heal allies for 100%% of its damage values during daytime.
5479.name: Illuminate

5497.scepterDescription: Reduces cooldown and causes Shadow Dance active to be an area of effect ability, hiding nearby allied heroes underneath it.
5497.name: Shadow Dance

5505.scepterDescription: Causes Mystic Snake to turn enemies into stone for %stone_form_scepter_base% second, increases by  %stone_form_scepter_increment% seconds per bounce.
5505.name: Mystic Snake

5517.scepterDescription: Heroes affected by Stampede take reduced damage, and are able to run through obstructions, including trees and up cliffs.
5517.name: Stampede

5518.scepterDescription: Increases travel distance and speed, and causes Shockwave to come back. Return wave slows units, but deals half damage to creeps.
5518.name: Shockwave

5548.scepterDescription: Viscous Nasal Goo becomes a no target area of effect ability, applying to all enemies within range.
5548.name: Viscous Nasal Goo

5584.scepterDescription: Anytime Skywrath Mage casts an ability, a different random nearby target will be hit with the same ability. Heroes will take priority.
5584.name: Mystic Flare

5588.scepterDescription: Increases duration. While Borrowed Time is active, a percentage of all damage taken by allied Heroes in a radius will be redirected to Abaddon.
5588.name: Borrowed Time

5594.scepterDescription: Increases slow duration, and units pulled in by Earth Splitter are also disarmed.
5594.name: Earth Splitter

5598.scepterDescription: Increases Duel duration, makes Legion Commander Spell Immune in Duel, and makes Legion Commander and her opponent only take damage from each other.
5598.name: Duel

5615.scepterDescription: Causes bonus damage to be granted to nearby allied heroes for half the values.
5615.name: Atrophy Aura

5630.scepterDescription: Increases number of attacks to destroy Supernova and allows Phoenix to cast Supernova on an allied hero, bringing both into the sun to be reborn together. Does not refresh ultimate abilities.
5630.name: Supernova

5639.scepterDescription: Reduces cooldown and improves cast point.
5639.name: Purifying Flames

5651.scepterDescription: Causes Arctic Burn to be a toggle ability, draining 40 mana per second when active. Removes limit on number of attacks per target.
5651.name: Arctic Burn
